## 11. v0 known gaps (frozen, must not compound)

- No outbound DTO validation in any current route (finding #17 — `app/api/projects/route.ts:25` returns `result.unwrap()` raw).
- No Stripe response validation in `app/api/stripe/verify/route.ts` (finding #18).
- No AI streamed-JSON validation in `lib/ai-service.ts` (finding #19) — invalid JSON is silently skipped, side effects (credit deduct) run anyway.

These are **frozen**: no new code may add to the count. New routes ship with full inbound + outbound validation. New AI integrations ship with response schemas.

